MinLengthError.ErrorText: Response must be at least {MinLength} characters long.

MaxLengthError.ErrorText: Response can be at most {MaxLength} characters long.

MinValueError.ErrorText: Value must be greater than or equal to {MinValue}.

MaxValueError.ErrorText: Value must be less than or equal to {MaxValue}.

InvalidDateTimeError.ErrorText: Response must be a valid date/time.

InvalidIntegerError.ErrorText: Response must be a whole number

InvalidPositiveIntegerError.ErrorText: Response must be a whole number greater than or equal to zero.

InvalidFloatError.ErrorText: Response must be a decimal number.

RegExValidationError.ErrorText: Response does not match required format.

AuthenticationError.ErrorText: Survey login failed. Please make sure the entire survey link or URL has been selected. If you have entered login values using your keyboard, please review these values for any mistakes. Please contact the organization hosting this survey if you feel this situation is in error.

AlreadySubmittedError.ErrorText:
This survey has already been taken for the specified user.

Please contact your survey administrator if you feel this situation is in error.

DuplicateCredentialsError.ErrorText:
A survey configuration problem has been detected.

Please report this problem to the organization hosting this survey.

SessionTimeoutError.ErrorText:
Your survey session has expired.

Your previous responses have been saved. To resume your survey session please select the
original survey link or URL used to start this survey. Contact your survey administrator if
you have troubles resuming your survey session.

InvalidEmailAddressError.ErrorText:
The email address '{SAVEPAGEEMAILADDRESS}' is not valid.
Please enter a valid email address.

EmailSendError.ErrorText:
There was a problem sending to this email address.
Please enter a valid email address.

EmailSentMessage.ErrorText: The email has been sent successfully.

ExclusiveCheckError.ErrorText: Please do not check '{0}' if other answers to the question are checked.

JavaScriptRequiredError.ErrorText:
This survey requires a more recent browser that supports JavaScript version 1.4 or higher.

To continue with the survey make sure JavaScript is enabled and refresh/reload the current page.
If you are using a version of Internet Explorer or Netscape earlier than 6.0 you will need to upgrade.

LoopFollowUpRequiredError.ErrorText: Question #{QNum} requires all item(s) to be answered.

SurveyHookValidationError.ErrorText: A general survey configuration error was detected. Please contact the administrator of this survey for further assistance.

To begin, please click the start button below.

TextHtml.name: T4
TextHtml.TextHtmlValue:
In this next task, we would like to see how quickly you can respond to the words RED and GREEN. For this task, you will need to place your hands on the keyboard. If possible, place one index finger on the letter F, one index finger on the letter J, and one or both thumbs on the space bar. The letter F means STOP. The letter J means GO. The space bar allows you to advance to the next screen. If you hit the space bar while you can see the word RED or GREEN, you will skip to the next item.

 

Please press the space bar to continue.

TextHtml.name: T5
T6
TextHtml.TextHtmlValue:
For example, if you see:
Press F for “stop,” J for “go,” or the space bar to skip to the next screen.

RED


You should press the letter F. Please do this now.

TextHtml.name: T7
TextHtml.TextHtmlValue:
And if you see:
Press F for “stop,” J for “go,” or the space bar to skip to the next screen.

GREEN

You should press the letter J. Please do this now.
